function xml(s){ return String(s==null?'':s).replace(/[&<>"]/g,function(c){return({'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;'})[c];}); }
const courseTitle = meta.title || meta.topic || 'Awareness Module';
const orgId = 'jarvis.' + base;
const manifest = '<?xml version="1.0" standalone="no"?>\n'
 + '<manifest identifier="' + xml(orgId) + '.manifest" version="1.2"\n'
 + '  xmlns="http://www.imsproject.org/xsd/imscp_rootv1p1p2"\n'
